Well, I spoke too soon.

On the way to work this morning, the new oil filter they put on
exploded. I am getting the feeling that the oil pump valve is sticking
and the pressure is building to a *slightly* unacceptable level. It is
back in the shop to get the spring checked.

Yeah! I love my bus! :(

